### 검수 시작 - 정상
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/inspections/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/start
X-User-Id: 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000099

### 검수 시작 - 존재하지 않는 inspectionId
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/inspections/99999999-9999-9999-9999-999999999999/start
X-User-Id: 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000099
